  <summary>Open Design for Linux</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Unofficial Linux packaging of Open Design, an AI-native design tool.</p>
    <p>This package is built from the upstream macOS DMG and rebuilt for Linux: the Electron runtime is replaced with the matching Linux build and the native better-sqlite3 module is compiled from source for the target Electron ABI.</p>
  </description>
